Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜里 在不经意间闻到花香时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就感到仿佛要想起什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 又总是想不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那似是令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又似是令人恐惧的某种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:55.66,title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2500,0)\p1\c&H49F4ED&\pos(235,500)}m 0 0 l -500 0 l -500 100 l 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:55.66,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(2500,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\fs65\pos(222,83)}散发芳香的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这雨太大 我没法赶路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便让我借宿一晚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来歇着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你是虫师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果碰上了什么怪事或是身体有不舒服的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不定能帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不知道啊 我们全家的长处就是身体好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说头疼的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是天天干活没得偷闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你是旅行者 那就说说其他地方的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经很久没离开过这个村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听到那么多不寻常的事 我也觉得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们过得都很平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平安无事是最好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快点回去 要不她会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花的香味…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又感觉自己像是忘记了什么重要的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地方以前有这个洞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有人挖的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花香…是从这里传出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这里是不是会通往别的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个方向说不定是回村的近道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉要被花香闷得喘不过气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底忘记了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 记得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久 很久之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行 你们差不多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口碑不是都一年不如一年了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我加工钱就酿出更好的酒来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 现在的工钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还敢顶嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 把那个捡一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙搞什么嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还撒谎！薰都说他看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 一句道歉都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就给我滚出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都漏光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰 该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 那女孩好像在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 她究竟是谁来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才 突然有一种十分怀念的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你背
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 好像有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 到底是哪里不对劲…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了 又想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 这个洞我以前也见过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花香…是从这里传出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这里应该能通往别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不她会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又好像快要想起什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段时间总觉得不太对头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一直住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却常常有种十分怀念的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行 你们差不多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的事之前也发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…是那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 她是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个情景我也见过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在很久 很久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 很久之前究竟是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是 无论如何也想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这雨太大 我没法赶路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便让我借宿一晚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你是虫师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果碰上了什么怪事或是身体有不舒服的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不定能帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不知道啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你是叫银古吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 我心里一直有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打从我记事起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就常常觉得应该是第一次发生的事曾经见过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得同样的事以前也发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在…也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也让你在这样的雨夜留宿过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我这是头一次到这附近来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这倒也没什么影响
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是总觉得心神不宁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道这种事是不是本来就偶尔会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既视感…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚闻到花香就觉得不安？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像忘记了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你或许是被「回陋」给困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一种会散发出花香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引昆虫或者野兽进入的黑筒状的虫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 据说这种虫会将被引入的猎物的时间扭曲成环状
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猎物就会重复地活在同一段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人有办法确认是不是确实是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果真是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你应该已经经历过许多次同样的人生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且 之后你还会再碰上回陋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你对此没有意识 再一次走了进去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么时间就会重来 你又会经历同样的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然记录上能找到拥有既视感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但毕竟无法做彻底的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得知那个人人生的每个细节是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在…重复同样的事…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法断定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你最好小心会发出花香的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被回陋困住的人随心所欲地改变了过去的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 拥有了既视感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许也就意味着你无法和以前一样回到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果穿行的次数太多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能会在不知不觉间和回陋同化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别再往里钻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我的确有想要改变的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我更想看到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如长大成人的女儿 孙子的小脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那些从未见过的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 郁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去摘野菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好几次钻进了这个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后回到了过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回来得这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个你是我从来没见到过的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像…一直在做着幸福的恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢 究竟怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都会是新的一天的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 郁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郁…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就带你去找大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郁的身体在渐渐冷下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这么下去 不等回村就要——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别再往里钻了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…听我说 郁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个洞里传出了花香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是回村的近道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后又会在遥远的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起生活的……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才 好像快想起什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郁 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟…是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像 既让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又让人恐惧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这雨太大 我没法赶路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便让我借宿一晚吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 残红
